data.description: Welcome to this charming traditional home situated in Swatara Township! Totaling over 1,440 of finished living space, this home is ready to welcome its new owner. Step inside and you will find a large family room, perfect for entertaining! Next on the first floor you will find the kitchen and dining room, along with a bonus room that could be utilized as a primary bedroom or anything your heart desires! On the second floor you will find 3 bedrooms and a full bath. Outside you will find a deck, perfect for your outside enjoyment. Recent updates include a new roof and new furnace! A joy to own!
